extends base.pug

block style
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="/static/styleAcademy.css")

block content 
    section#academyHero
        div.hero-content
            h1 The Academy
            p.tagline Precision Engineering in Every Movement

    section.stats-bar
        div.stat-item
            h2 5000+
            p Sq. Ft. Studio
        div.stat-item
            h2 10+
            p Elite Mentors
        div.stat-item
            h2 100%
            p Performance Focus

    section.info-section
        div.info-container
            div.info-text
                h2 Architectural Movement
                p Established by developers from NIT Raipur, Kinetic Artistry is the first studio to apply structural engineering principles to contemporary dance. We believe that every movement must have a solid foundation, much like the backend of a robust application.
                p Our facility is engineered for high-performance training, featuring professional-grade impact-absorbing flooring and integrated audio systems designed for acoustic perfection.
            div.info-visual
                //- This will be a high-end CSS-styled box in styleAcademy.css
                div.visual-accent-box
                    span Structure
                    span & 
                    span Soul

    section.mission-grid
        div.mission-card
            h3 The Blueprint
            p Every syllabus is designed with algorithmic precision to ensure student progress is linear and measurable.
        div.mission-card
            h3 The Infrastructure
            p Our studio utilizes industrial-grade equipment to provide a safe and professional environment for all ages.
        div.mission-card
            h3 The Scalability
            p From basic foundations to professional stage presence, we provide a learning path that scales with your ambition.